title Sequence Diagram — Alur Transaksi NFC di Kantin

actor "Siswa\n(Kartu NFC)" as Siswa <<siswa>>
participant "App POS Mobile\n(Petugas Kantin)" as POS <<petugas>>
participant "Supabase Database\n(Backend Server)" as DB <<admin>>

note over POS: Petugas memilih produk\nke keranjang (Cart)\n+ biaya kustom (opsional)

Siswa -> POS : 1. Tap Kartu RFID/NFC
activate POS

POS -> DB : 2. Query siswa by Card UID
activate DB
DB --> POS : 3. Return Nama, Foto, Saldo Teraktual
deactivate DB

note over POS: 4. Cek lokal:\nSaldo >= Total Keranjang?

alt Saldo Cukup (Saldo >= Total Belanja)
  POS -> DB : 5. Kirim data transaksi\n(student_id, item list, total belanja)
  activate DB

  note over DB: 6. Server-Side Validation (ACID):\n1. Query saldo riil teraktual\n2. Cek saldo >= total belanja riil\n3. Validasi harga produk dari tabel products\n4. Potong saldo (UPDATE students SET balance)\n5. Simpan ke transactions & transaction_items\n6. CHECK constraint: balance >= 0

  alt Verifikasi Server Sukses
    DB -> DB : Commit transaksi DB
    DB --> POS : 7. Return Transaksi Sukses & Saldo Sisa
    deactivate DB

    POS --> Siswa : 8. Tampil Sukses & Haptic Getar ✅
    DB -> Siswa : 9. Push Notification ke HP Siswa (FCM)

  else Verifikasi Server Gagal (Data Tampered / Hack)
    DB --> POS : Error: Transaksi Tidak Valid (Ditolak Server)
    deactivate DB
    POS --> Siswa : Transaksi Dibatalkan ⚠️
  end

else Saldo Tidak Cukup (Saldo < Total Belanja)
  note over POS: UI berubah Merah\nTombol Terkunci
  POS --> Siswa : Layar POS Merah — Transaksi Ditolak ❌
end

deactivate POS

@enduml
